outputs.output_descr: The objective of the project is to improve the coverage and effectiveness of protected areas in the Central Tian Shan Mountains so as to expand threatened species representation in the national system (the snow leopard).

project_descr: Project Preparation Grant: Improving the coverage and management effectiveness of Protected Areas in the Central Tian Shan Mountains. This Initiation Plan seeks to elaborate the final medium-sized project proposal.
project_title: PROTECTED AREAS IN CENTRAL TIAN SHAN MOUNTAINS
